---
title: Peppercorn Beef & Caramelised Onion Gravy with Garlic Veggie Mash & Tomato Salad
description: There are some hidden gems in tonight’s dinner. The juicy beef rump has been cooked in a peppercorn coating for
an extra punch, an easy way to make this dish decadent. And this isn’t any ordinary mash, we’ve added carrot and
garlic to bring it to the next level. While we’re going all out, drizzle over a caramelised onion gravy and your taste
buds will be feeling very spoilt.

